{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "登台致禮", "storyInfo": "劇團長回顧此前在地塊上發生的一切，大肆宣講他關於“死亡”的美學。而盧西恩表明來意——再一次殺死他。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_sys_act43side_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drkcludsthdr", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g5_duelscene", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "破壞了你的演出，我深表遺憾。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如若你是指自己解決了那個名叫莫伊拉的孩子……那我應當譴責你不合時宜的謙遜，盧西恩。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以你之穎悟，應該猜到了故事原本的結局。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一樁五年前的舊案，一場恰到好處的天災，風暴與遲來的審判同時降臨在這個地塊……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那個原本游離於故事之外的札拉克，慢慢走到了舞台中央，殺死所有背負著罪孽的人。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "盧西恩", "content": "爾後，她將意識到自己的所作所為不過是基於一種虛妄的執念，她將清醒，她將萬念俱灰，她將審判最後一人——"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "盧西恩", "end": "true", "content": "她自己。", "joined": "爾後，她將意識到自己的所作所為不過是基於一種虛妄的執念，她將清醒，她將萬念俱灰，她將審判最後一人——她自己。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你呢？", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是劇本中偶然經過的信使，你是劇組裡無足輕重的新人，你離核心矛盾如此遙遠，卻在最終成了所有線索的句點。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“偶然”越出人意料，那無從更改的“必然”上演時，越是震撼人心……這便是戲劇的魅力，你我早已無數次領略。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以啊，你並未破壞什麼，你只是在為演出增色。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就像你曾在劇團的所作所為。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我途經這種種慘劇，只是為了走向你。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，當然。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#12$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拍賣會上的一個劇團印記，並不足以讓你確認我的存在，對吧？", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#12$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時隔多年，“死亡”，抑或說“毀滅”，依然是你善用的橋段，鍾愛的結局。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子啊孩子，我多麼希望，你由衷認可它的美。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由衷認可嗎……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不至於，劇團長。我只是比誰都熟悉它。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我演過很多戲，我殺過很多人，我的雙手滿是鮮血。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我幼時便接受的教育，這是你灌輸給我的人生。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是我最好的學生，盧西恩。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在最後的高潮戲到來前，且讓我們回顧此前的演出吧。你我都對這個流程再熟悉不過。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長微笑著向盧西恩優雅鞠躬，他尾巴捲起的權杖遙指向越來越逼近的天災雲，像是一支沾滿墨汁的筆……"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熟悉的景象在盧西恩眼前展開。他知道自己無從拒絕，不，他為此而來。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩輕輕頷首。"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，首先是道爾頓。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i01_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 1.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blackmask", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "fi"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "fi", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對這個行屍走肉般的中年演員而言，這場戲原本無足輕重。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貢獻幾分難得的清醒，調動僅剩的已成本能的技巧，背誦不多的台詞，熬到導演喊停，換取足以支撐下一個長夜的酒錢……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他從未哀悼那個因自己而死的女演員，從未緬懷意氣風發的曾經，甚至不會因如今的潦倒失意有所羞慚。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你操縱了他。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誠然，沒有我的介入，他不會主動找到那把被調換了的刀，並交到你的手中……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我並未命令他將胸膛迎向刀鋒。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你與他對戲的那一刻，他已然清醒，已然知曉自己身處怎樣的危險之中。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩，戲劇到電影的轉換，絲毫沒有妨礙你自如地揮灑自己的天賦。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的表演喚醒了他的記憶，你讓他想起自己曾是一名多麼優秀的演員——沉浸其中，賦予虛擬的喜怒哀樂以真實。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一刻，“信使”入了戲，“杜邦爵士”也徹底被破產的可能性扭曲了內心……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他必須掩蓋真相，他必須拼盡全力殺死眼前人，卻忽略了刀鋒可能反過來傷到自己……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當時就在他的對面，沒有人比你更清楚，那一刻，他的憤怒與恐懼多麼有感染力。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為謝幕演出，近乎完美。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，近在咫尺的死亡，反而激起了他被酒精麻痺許久的勝負慾，他盡情表演，意興盎然！", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_62_i03", "style": "cg", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.2, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i03", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有邁克爾與瑪麗昂。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拈花惹草的演員與精明的服裝師被雙雙吊在拍攝現場，他們那可笑的私情就這麼被攤在所有人面前。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的結合可恥而滑稽，他們放縱自己的慾望，醉心於巴結有權勢的人，互相鄙夷卻又互相利用……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們身上從內到外看不見一絲真實，那個邁克爾，甚至連耳朵和尾巴都是偽造的。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的死毫無價值，除了為那個攝影助理提供了一則可以兜售的八卦。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，盧西恩，你查看過現場，那隻貓也舔拭過此地殘留的情緒——", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該清楚，當莫伊拉敲響這扇門，當死亡的腳步聲逼近，在那不容思索的片刻間，他們各自做了什麼。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "淚痕。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，有趣的細節。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾的眼角留有淚痕，“洛克菲勒”三兄弟的任意一位都未曾向“杜邦夫人”表露過這般深情……", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這把消防斧原本是砍向瑪麗昂的。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾保護了她，將自身的要害暴露在了利刃之下。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在生命的最後關頭，這對前一刻仍在互相攻訐的男女，下意識的反應是守護彼此。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "fi", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_62_i03"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g5_duelscene", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們確認了對彼此的，真情。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本身並不值得歌頌。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得沒錯，我的孩子。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#12$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，觀眾已經落座，他們期待在這燈光與聲響圍築成的幻夢中看到什麼？", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "攀附權勢者到頭來一無所有，縱慾者終被慾望反噬？當然，這是最順理成章的編排，用以展示一些無聊的大道理。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們何曾想過，並不值得歌頌的真情也足以讓人意外。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩人又何曾想過，他們有那麼一刻，會為彼此動容。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡賦予他們可能？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡賦予他們可能。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，還有莫伊拉——在你現身之前，我最看好的孩子。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 1.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i04_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blackmask", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "fi"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉因另一人的死亡而重建了信念。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那人的名字、生平、飲食習慣與標誌性的微笑，悽慘的死狀與逍遙法外的兇手們……莫伊拉銘記“勞拉”的一切。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她悲慟，她憤怒，她質疑，她仇恨，她油然而生的一切情緒，點燃了一段被塵封的過往，也點燃了她自己。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她主導了整場演出。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長，你何苦低估自己在其中的作用？", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你加入一紙即興創作，將一段本不存在的過往強塞進了她的腦海，將“勞拉”帶進了她的人生。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，那又如何？", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看看莫伊拉——", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在起舞。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩，你是她當時的舞伴，應該對此深有感觸——", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她並未像猩紅劇團的孩子們一樣，從小接受“白英花”的訓練，但你看她的舞步、她的形體、她臉上的哭泣與微笑……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在表演一種生活，抑或營造一種真實……或者，她再也沒有什麼局限，她可以是任何人。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她將在千百樣人生中起舞，永不落幕，直到軀殼與心神再也無法負載這種種情感。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或者，她終將遇見你，或其他偏愛真相的愚人，在某個夜晚恍然夢醒，結束自己的生命。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論結局為何，她的靈魂都曾豐盈而充實。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論結局為何……她都不再只是一個從開拓區來的舉目無親的小道具師，空無所依的札拉克。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "fi", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g5_duelscene", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是如此健談，劇團長。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已有許久不曾見你這般富有激情地評價他人。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……自你之後，盧西恩。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不否認我施加在莫伊拉身上的影響，我給了她一些激勵，就像我曾經給過你的一樣。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的孩子，你忘了嗎？", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如若不是對表演的渴望，你早已死去。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你在天災中流離失所，當你失去家園與雙親，當你在巨大的古堡與陌生的同伴間迷失，你說——", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "fi"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 1.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "pic_rogue_1_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL_castlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blackmask", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有當我是劇中角色時……", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的孤獨才能被消除……", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有自己的歸宿。", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "fi", "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_blackmask", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g5_duelscene", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以此為寄託，你因此得救。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你與莫伊拉——你們都是天生的演員，靠憑空創造的悲喜滋養自我。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無人可以忽視你們的光芒！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而孩子，死亡是你們共同的良師。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還記得嗎？那時你深陷瓶頸，表演上再難寸進，而周遭的一切無法給予你更多體悟……", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你毫不猶豫地將源石刺進了自己的喉嚨。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你感受到了死亡，那是最無可爭議的絕境！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它將恐懼、嫉妒、悲傷、憤怒、恥辱、貪婪……萬千於你而言太過陌生的情感帶給了你，它讓你的心在觀照萬千後，成為了明鏡。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它賦予你解構權威的立場、摧毀一切的決意、無止境的夜與不停止的歌……", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它讓不起眼的盧西恩，成為了耀眼的——猩紅血鑽！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“猩紅血鑽”……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "久遠的稱呼。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，想想道爾頓、邁克爾與瑪麗昂、勞拉與莫伊拉……看看那些在天災中掙扎的人們，還有你自己……", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得沒錯，死亡仍是我善用的橋段，鍾愛的結局。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我絕不視之為“毀滅”。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#5$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它讓偉大者自毀名節，讓苦修者打破戒律，讓聖潔者走入泥淖，讓英雄滿懷卑劣！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它讓失意者重新振奮，讓緘默者呼號理想，讓自私者流露哪怕一刻的真情，讓膽怯者超然忘我！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它讓先驅找到登高的台階，讓遠視者敢於放手一搏，讓自詡燈塔之人成為燈塔！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它培育意義，也澆灌缺陷；它鞏固真實，也餵養虛假；它讓垂死的血肉成為花朵，讓本應消失無痕的得到銘刻！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是無從排解的苦，也是盎然的靈感！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是戲劇的因與果，魂與肉，驅動創造的偉力，萬千主義、形式與探索無從逃離的“律”與“繩”……", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#3$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬物的歸宿！", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長看向盧西恩，微笑依然掛在他的嘴邊。風沙正急，而他不為所動。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，它也是你我重逢的契機。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drkcludsthdr", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clapsolo", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#12$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺憾，掌聲過於寥落。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#12$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站在你對面的，只有我……也只能是我。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘈雜的聲響從四面八方傳來，盧西恩仔細地聽著。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災在肆虐，Miss.Christine一反常態地低嘯，相識不久的同伴在驚惶奔走，無望地求救……"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如劇團長所說，死亡正在上演，從幾齣循序漸進的重頭戲，到整個舞台俯拾皆是。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說死亡是你我重逢的契機……我無比贊同。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我不會放過這次的機會。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請允許我在您回顧完畢後，發表一些自己的見解——你我都對這個流程再熟悉不過。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_avg_prts_intro", "key": "$m_avg_prts_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_land_impact", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風暴折斷了一截拍攝用的鋼架，火星四濺，兩人附近的一塊地毯被點燃，火焰緊貼著盧西恩的身旁跳動。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但盧西恩毫不在意，他緊盯著面前的人，脫帽頷首。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_062cg_phantom_front", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_062cg_phantom_bihand", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i08", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.15, "yScaleTo": 1.15, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自你現身起，為何隻字未提我對你不只一次的背叛？", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（微笑）", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為那並不重要，因為你還是你，孩子。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迷狂又清醒，出走又歸來……飽經曲折後的重逢是多麼難能可貴，一切齟齬都可以被歲月原諒。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是這樣嗎？", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾以為，劇團是你的筆、你的網，混亂的世道和在演出中尋求慰藉的觀眾為你張目，所以無人能從你手中逃離。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以更早的時候，我與暮落還有劇作家的計劃失敗了。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時我年輕、稚拙而自負，我們自以為看破了劇團的真相，然而精心安排的脫逃，到頭來成了你演出的一環。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終，暮落帶著對你的恐懼繼續逃遁，而我重新走向你。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你回到了我的身邊。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是自那一刻起，你決意學習我所有的技巧，熟諳劇團的一切，然後瓦解它。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以死亡了斷死亡，以毀滅終結毀滅。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“白英花”、“刀舞”、“影子”……那些曾予你教誨的老師們，盡皆死於你手。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還有我。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猶記得自己當時破裂張狂的歌喉，以及刀鋒刺入你胸膛的溫熱，我自以為毀掉了整個猩紅劇團……", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕做到這種程度，我依然失敗了，不是嗎？", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有死去。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為死亡常在，而戲劇永恆。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "永恆，是啊，那之後，我花費了更多時間研究你的作品——包括我自己。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我窮盡你的永恆，像一個魯鈍的信徒。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終，我走到了這裡。再一次身臨你引以為傲的戲劇，盛大的死亡、悲劇與美學……", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到此刻，天災為你我搭好最後的舞台。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長，尊敬的老師，或者更準確一點，我應該稱呼你為，“酒神”。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將毀掉你的一切。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩解開了喉間的抑制器，暴露的源石結晶閃耀著，像是為即將到來的歌唱雀躍。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他朝劇團長深深鞠躬，雲層在他身後傾倒。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}